---
// Writing — nrbts.world
// A dedicated, static text-reading page for Norbert's personal running-
// journal pieces. Deliberately has NO Three.js scene: the whole point of
// this page is long-form reading, and running the live parallax city/sky
// behind it would only cost battery/perf for zero benefit (mobile-
// performance constraint). Shares the same type system and color tokens
// as index.astro (Chakra Petch + Sora, teal/purple accents, cut-corner
// light panels on a dark ground) so it still reads as the same site, just
// a quieter room in it.
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>Writing — nrbts.world</title>
		<meta name="description" content="Selected running pieces by Norbert Sauter — a marathon rematch a decade later, a trail-race stumble, and a Nike Pegasus Trail 5 GTX review." />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
		<link
			href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Chakra+Petch:wght@500;600;700&family=Sora:wght@400;500;600&display=swap"
			rel="stylesheet"
		/>
